Option 1: The Spreadsheet Formula (Best for Import)
Use this formula to generate an 8-character ID that looks exactly like a standard AppSheet UNIQUEID().

The Formula:

Excel
=LOWER(DEC2HEX(RANDBETWEEN(0, 4294967295), 8))
